						               													<description>The game of Kryptik can be played by 2 players in our standard format, 4 players in our more casual Krucible format, and requires nothing more than some Kryptik decks to get started. No need for dice, tokens, special mats, or boards. This immaculate card game design allows players to adopt the game more easily and gives players/store owners the option to put on draft or sealed deck events with (literally) just a booster box and some friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each game of Kryptik represents your life on Kryptik Island. You are a citizen with 66 years to prove your worth to the Overseers, and these years are represented by your six 11 year cards. You must work towards victory by slinging spells and commanding your citizen allies to attack your opponent in an effort to destroy all of their 11 year cards. Hit them one more time after you destroy their final 11 year card and you win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
